snippet.title: Aussie Athletes Held, Fined over Credential Flap
snippet.description:
Nine Australian athletes were detained by Rio de Janeiro police in a flap over credentials at an Olympic basketball game. The athletes were released after apologizing to authorities and agreeing to pay a fine, a team official said Saturday. (Aug. 20)

snippet.title: Glover's 'Atlanta' is a slice of American life
snippet.description:
Donald Glover talks about letting the "Internet" name is latest show 'Atlanta,' and says that he thinks the city the show is named after is the most representative of America. (Aug. 20)
